piwik (2.16.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.16.0

 -- Michael Gebetsroither <mgebetsroither@mgit.at>  Thu, 25 Feb 2016 17:12:48 +0100

piwik (2.15.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.15.0
  * Make theme look great when used in Mobile browser (Closes: #5029)
  * Implement "Content Security Policy" (CSP) (Closes: #1542)
  * Format numbers displayed in Piwik reports (eg. 1,000,000 instead of
    1000000) (Closes: #1254)
  * Disable 'Provider' plugin by default for new Piwik users (tracker
    performance) [by @mattab, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8826)
  * Make Piwik opt-out feature work on internet explorer 11 when third
    party cookies are disabled (Closes: #8578)
  * Release AnonymousPiwikUsageMeasurement plugin on the Marketplace
    (Closes: #9051)
  * New Piwik design when main menu is on the left [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #7589)
  * On databases that have a default charset that is not utf-8, data can
    get corrupted [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6497)
  * New Awesome Search bar in Piwik (Closes: #8946)
  * Major progress in PHP7 Compatibility for Piwik (Closes: #8893)
  * New Command 'core:invalidate-report-data' to invalidate archive data
    (w/ period cascading) [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #8825)
  * Display the "Segmented Visitor Log" icon in Custom Variables report
    (Closes: #8755)
  * New diagnostic command 'diagnostics:analyze-archive-table' that
    analyzes archive tables [by @diosmosis, @tsteur] (Closes: #8625)
  * Allow plugin developers to get their plugins translated by the piwik
    community [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7883)
  * Improved diagnostics: new LogViewer plugin in Marketplace! (Closes:
    #7239)
  * Make it easier to create Segments with Custom Variables [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #6031)
  * New segments: Download file URL 'downloadUrl' and Outlink URL
    'outlinkUrl' [by @mattab] (Closes: #4103)
  * New website setting: Only track visits and actions when the action
    URL starts with one of the above URLs [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #588)
  * SQL query to find websites with traffic since last successful
    archiving can take 6+ hours [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8066)
  * In SQL queries, print out the name of the plugin in a SQL comment
    for troubleshooting which plugin triggered query (Closes: #7913)
  * Use the "Left Menu" as default menu for all Piwik users (Closes:
    #7169)
  * Two factor authentication login: new GoogleAuthenticator plugin on
    Marketplace! (Closes: #2846)
  * Improve date selector usability [by @tsteur] (Closes: #8864)
  * New command 'database:optimize-archive-tables' to optimize archive
    tables (even if on InnoDB). [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #8633)
  * Archiving performance: cache the slow segment subqueries that are
    using LIKE constraint [by @mattab] (Closes: #8850)
  * Update some of UI icons with new set of font icons [by @mnapoli,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #7618)
  * a multilingual Glossary using Piwik translations, available from
    your "Help" page and glossary.piwik.org [by @mattab] (Closes: #6773)
  * New design for Administration Left menu (Closes: #7588)
  * Row Evolution can fail when a segment is used (Closes: #8776)
  * How do I enable debug logging in Piwik Tracker? (Closes: #8593)
  * Chrome's "Data Saver" mode prevents tracking of many visitors using
    Chrome browser (Closes: #7733)
  * PageURL Segmentation fails on the ecommerce page [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #6593)
  * When AdBlock Plus is used, suggest user to disable it for Piwik
    (Closes: #5094)
  * Use Piwik to measure how Piwik app is used by the community (opt-in)
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #4589)
  * Display 'Report generated Xs ago' in help tooltip [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #9075)
  * Tracker configId should be based on original IP, not on anonymised
    IP? (Closes: #7778)
  * Do not merge assets when specific URL parameter
    &disable_merged_assets=1 is set [by @ThaDafinser, @tsteur, @mattab]
    (Closes: #8529)
  * Refactor tracker code for clarity, modularity and so plugins can
    have more granular control over tracking [by @diosmosis, @mattab]
    (Closes: #8317)
  * UsersManager add form inputs use placeholders instead of values [by
    @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8628)
  * Prevent content spoofing: display error if the URL is not valid
    (Closes: #8693)
  * remove extra line break and indentation in Admin UI [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #4615)
  * invalidateArchivedReports API can invalidate report data for a
    particular '&segment=' (Closes: #8858)
  * Mobile Messaging: new SMS provider to help developers debug
    (available in development mode) [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes:
    #8773)
  * In each SQL query, when a segment is used, print the segment string
    in a SQL comment (Closes: #8752)
  * New method logAllContenBlocksOnPage to piwik.js that lets you debug
    which content blocks are on your page [by @diosmosis, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #8650)
  * Case-insensitive login [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8610)
  * Add option to set "process_new_segments_from" to
    "segment_last_edit_time" [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #8607)
  * Make it possible to donate to plugin creators from within piwik [by
    @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #8561)
  * Display total number of actions across all websites [by @mnapoli,
    @mattab] (Closes: #8550)
  * in Update settings, let user choose "Use the latest release" or "Use
    the Long Term Support release" [by @tsteur] (Closes: #8549)
  * Email reports: print the full URL source / origin of report in the
    email body (Closes: #8461)
  * During bulk tracking, return indices of invalid requests [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #8296)
  * Emoji in titles or URLs cause tracking to fail [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7766)
  * Do not use eval function in piwik.js (for CSP) (Closes: #5960)
  * Does Piwik support IPv6 protocol? (Closes: #8899)
  * Performance regression: All dimensions are created on each request
    [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8399)
  * New FAQs to document how to use Redis for sessions and cache
    (Closes: #7767)
  * Use improved tooltips for all tooltips in the visitor log [by
    @mnapoli, @tsteur] (Closes: #8545)
  * Update icons [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8488)
  * Piwik dashboard widgets are not aligned [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7847)
  * Help text for Content tracking metrics and dimensions [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #8945)
  * Improve number formats [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #8857)
  * Improve date & time formats [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #8856)
  * When saving plugin settings, disable the "Save" button to prevent
    double clicks [by @tsteur] (Closes: #8811)
  * Set HTML <title> values in all user menu and admin menu pages [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #8788)
  * Better logging messages in core:archive output [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #8777)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Fri, 06 Nov 2015 16:19:20 +1100

piwik (2.14.3-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.14.3
  * Install of 2.14.2 blocked by permissions check on piwik/config path
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #8439)
  * Overlay improvements [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes: #8431)
  * In Page Overlay sidebar, add icon to let me "Open segmented visitor
    log" [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #8352)
  * Improve design of Trusted Piwik Hostname setting [by @barbushin,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #8403)
  * Rename "Widgets & Dashboard" selector or change the selector [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7835)
  * Piwik errors logged in server error log should not have HTML [by
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #8293)
  * New config entry to set email name in email FROM field [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #8252)
  * Fix bug in notification angular directive, do not use data-binding
    for noclear attribute... [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #8472)
  * UserCountryMap plugin shows wrong options in countries select [by
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #8285)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 195 strings in 32 languages
    (sk, ar, de, ja, nl, nb, sv, be, bg, ca, cs, da, el, es, fa, fi, fr,
    hi, hu, id, it, ko, pl, pt, ro, ru, sq, sr, th, tl, uk, vi) [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #8432)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 254 strings in 37 languages
    (gl, nb, cs, it, sk, de, el, fr, lt, ar, bg, ca, da, es, et, fa, fi,
    he, hi, hr, id, ja, ko, nl, nn, pl, ro, ru, sl, sq, sr, sv, ta, th,
    tl, tr, vi) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #8474)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Fri, 07 Aug 2015 15:44:14 +1000

piwik (2.14.2-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.14.2
  * Column not found: 1054 Unknown column
    'log_visit.location_browser_lang' in 'field list'" [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #8304)
  * renderer format is not valid - fatal php error after 2.14.0 (Closes:
    #8365)
  * URL parameter for core:archive console command is ignored [by
    @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #8316)
  * Limit notifications of not authenticated sessions [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #8307)
  * Can't update GrabGravatar plugin [by @tsteur] (Closes: #8370)
  * node.className.split is not a function on tracking click on/near SVG
    element [by @dandv, @tsteur] (Closes: #8346)
  * CLI plugin generator doesn't intercept plugin description [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #8294)
  * Site Search report does not display tooltips with metrics
    documentation (Closes: #8257)
  * Browser info tooltip doesn't hide (Closes: #7768)
  * Add System check that checks that shell_exec function is enabled [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #8411)
  * The string General_Cancel was not loaded in javascript [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #8407)
  * Fix emails validation with unknown TLD [by @barbushin, @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #8400)
  * Travis system extraction part 1 [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #8379)
  * Tweaks to .travis.yml generator [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #8374)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 661 strings in 8 languages
    (nl, sv, de, es, ja, lt, pl, nb) [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #8376)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Tue, 28 Jul 2015 12:16:48 +1000

piwik (2.14.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.14.1
  * Do not perform an inner join when looking for archives to purge, it
    does not scale. [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #8331)
  * Report archives have tripled in size since update to 2.10 [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #7181)
  * Embedding widgets with token_auth does not work anymore [by @sgiehl,
    @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #8321)
  * API: make parameter filter_excludelowpop_value work in all cases [by
    @mattab, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8324)
  * Web cron archive.php is not working in some cases [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #8312)
  * misc/others/api_internal_call.php is broken [by @diosmosis, @mattab]
    (Closes: #8311)
  * Apache Error 500 in case of Detected browser engine was not found in
    $availableEngines [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #8289)
  * Do not use INI [proxy] settings when connecting to localhost or
    127.0.0.1 [by @mattab] (Closes: #8272)
  * Site Search report does not display tooltips with metrics
    documentation [by @barbushin, @mattab] (Closes: #8257)
  * Mobile Messaging shows error message when changing setting (Closes:
    #8245)
  * Adding/Editing a new goal doesn't update its "state" and some UI
    issues (Closes: #8244)
  * Visitor map NaN error in browser console (Closes: #8221)
  * Quotes in goal names are over-escaped [by @diosmosis, @mattab]
    (Closes: #7969)
  * Browser info tooltip doesnt hide [by @barbushin, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7768)
  * Cannot click links in visitor-log-lightbox [by @barbushin, @mattab]
    (Closes: #7382)
  * Make Auto update buttons bigger (Closes: #8305)
  * Update to Kartograph 0.8.2 [by @barbushin, @mattab] (Closes: #8350)
  * Adding PRIVACY.md file to document various ways to improve Privacy
    for visitors and Piwik admins [by @mattab, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #8343)
  * missing translation General_Next in javascript of SitesManager [by
    @parruc, @mattab] (Closes: #8303)
  * Update to Kartograph 0.8.2 [by @barbushin, @mattab] (Closes: #8283)
  * Fixes duplication `onchange` event for `radio` elements [by
    @barbushin, @mattab] (Closes: #8248)
  * Add OptOutManager [by @Zeichen32, @mattab] (Closes: #8229)
  * Document the possible issue with data not being tracked and SSL
    certificates / net::ERR_INSECURE_RESPONSE (Closes: #8220)
  * Use translated plugin description if available [by @sgiehl, @mattab]
    (Closes: #8208)
  * Allow to test all API endpoints using SystemTestCase::runApiTests
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #8188)
  * Improve logging for "unexpected website" [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #7698)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 306 strings in 16 languages
    (sk, de, es, nb, sv, sl, el, fr, it, bg, cs, ko, nl, nn, pt, sq) [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #8334)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 18 Jul 2015 15:55:18 +1000

piwik (2.14.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.14.0
  * Implement CLI command to precisely delete raw data by date and
    idsite [by @mattab] (Closes: #6785)
  * Track file download and outlinks when user does a right click [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #5287)
  * Allow CLI archiving for only specific segments [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #7912)
  * Record hash tag for outgoing clicks (eg. mega.co.nz outlinks) [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #6244)
  * New segment 'language' [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #3950)
  * Expand Outlinks / Downloads if only one domain given [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7891)
  * Auto-update the referrer spammer blacklist [by @mnapoli, @mattab]
    (Closes: #8186)
  * Support Ping requests to report a better 'time on page' (Closes:
    #2041)
  * Segment userId should allow to use all operators including Contains
    operator =@ [by @mattab] (Closes: #8062)
  * Rename Ecommerce & Goals Category Titles [by @spacenate, @tsteur,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7885)
  * Make the installation of Piwik work with HHVM. [by @Loscillo,
    @mattab] (Closes: #8131)
  * New design for buttons [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7896)
  * New design for default tables [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #7895)
  * New design for the installation [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7875)
  * New design for alerts and notifications [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #7874)
  * New design for code blocks [by @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7793)
  * New design for Marketplace (in Administration) [by @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7586)
  * New design for Installer screens [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7584)
  * Improve the look of our data tables and of our report pages in
    general [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7090)
  * use consistent colours for fonts and buttons (Closes: #4495)
  * Make Popovers slightly wider [by @mattab] (Closes: #7517)
  * Piwik logo on IE9 is misplaced [by @tsteur] (Closes: #8190)
  * Some widgets have wrong styles in widget preview (headline etc) [by
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #7879)
  * Edit personal email report - Report hour is not readable on Firefox
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7827)
  * Use a card like design in dashboard [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #8191)
  * Popover displaying messages should use Piwik design style [by
    @mattab, @mnapoli] (Closes: #8087)
  * New design for the site manager [by @mnapoli, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #8002)
  * New design for forms [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #7960)
  * Redesign visitor log (Closes: #7909)
  * CSS and UI components demo [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7787)
  * New design for Administration screens [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7587)
  * Align numbers to the right of the columns [by @tsteur] (Closes:
    #4789)
  * The pragma "disableCookies" does not work in some browsers [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7494)
  * Very slow SQL queries when archiving a segment for an unknown action
    (Closes: #8102)
  * Details cut-off on Visitor Log modal pop-up (screenshot included)
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #7812)
  * Make sure to escape error messages [by @tsteur] (Closes: #8197)
  * While loading Piwik, the top menu displays all language names in a
    row for 1 second [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7736)
  * Disallow api content to be loaded within Piwik [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #8182)
  * Create a page that lists all available tracker SDKs for "universal"
    properties (Closes: #8039)
  * Installation Error Barnes_&_Noble.ico [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #8029)
  * Moved Intl data translations to a new plugin [by @sgiehl, @mattab]
    (Closes: #8017)
  * Document Ecommerce JavaScript Tracking API functions in API
    reference [by @mattab] (Closes: #7977)
  * fix core folder with php-cs-fixer for psr-2 [by @fabiocarneiro,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7956)
  * link tag (shortcut icon) generated twice in
    Morpheus/templates/layout.twig [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7897)
  * Remove UserSettings Plugin [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7846)
  * Report classes should not be instantiated directly [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7821)
  * Tracking code generator: Allow to generate tracking code for mobile
    apps etc. (Closes: #7803)
  * Create and maintain up-to-date the Piwik Roadmap (Closes: #7624)
  * noindex, nofollow option [by @mattab, @mnapoli, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #6552)
  * Show Piwik version on demo [by @mattab] (Closes: #5197)
  * Geo location with GeoIP PECL ISP database: correctly set the
    provider name [by @splinter89, @mattab] (Closes: #8174)
  * When searching for websites in the Sites Manger show all fields [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #8166)
  * Invalid link after uploading a plugin (Closes: #8136)
  * Make sure BulkTracking skips requests for non existant sites. [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #8132)
  * Fix missing variable escaping in the JS tracking code generator [by
    @mnapoli, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8109)
  * Added 'mbstring.func_overload = 0' check as installation requirement
    [by @barbushin, @mnapoli] (Closes: #8104)
  * NaN in VisitorMap when we have unknown regions (Closes: #8081)
  * Piwik is overlapping graph labels when viewport is too narrow
    (Closes: #8075)
  * API SitesManager.getSitesIdFromSiteUrl should match both HTTP and
    HTTPS websites [by @mattab] (Closes: #8070)
  * Popup displayed after changing visualization to cities while using
    the visitor map (Closes: #8061)
  * Visitor map visualization issues [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #8060)
  * Translate of Longitude column dimension is wrong [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7995)
  * Segmented Visitor Log icon does not show data when Page URL contains
    HTML entities [by @mattab] (Closes: #7989)
  * Provider submenu label may appear untranslated
    (Provider_SubmenuLocationsProvider) (Closes: #7985)
  * Console init failure when no config exist [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #7968)
  * Invalid URL fragment encoding (Closes: #7961)
  * When using old data purger, content tracking names are being
    deleted. (Closes: #7958)
  * Incorrect screen resolution detected for devices with device pixel
    ratio > 1 [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7941)
  * Map labels truncated for countries with no visits [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #7940)
  * Reusing a piwik database created a report that it had been updated
    to the same version [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7924)
  * Visitor Profile Widget should not be visible to anonymous users [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7899)
  * Getting Piwik to work on IE8 again by fixing a few issues [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #7886)
  * All Websites dashboard shows only the first 50 websites [by @tsteur,
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #7854)
  * Average order value graph [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7851)
  * sh: ps: not found in logs [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #7815)
  * Marketplace when closing popover it scrolls to top [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #7798)
  * No longer possible to change the dashboard layout to multiple
    columns [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7796)
  * Column Headers Missing in TSV / CSV data exports [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #7774)
  * Delete old visitor logs uses idvisit instead of the date [by
    @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #7180)
  * Visit Overview (with graph) widget scroll to wrong position under
    circumstances (Closes: #7086)
  * Outlinks not properly encoded [by @mattab] (Closes: #5014)
  * Remove keywords widget from the default dashboard [by @mattab]
    (Closes: #8189)
  * New automated test to detect when the Piwik files become too big [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #8158)
  * Move more i18n data translations to Intl plugin [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #8101)
  * Adding ping=1 tracker query param to allow JS tracker to update the
    end of visit time for more accurate visit length [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #8069)
  * Instant log output for failing UI tests and some tweaks on detection
    of page activity [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #8094)
  * Migrate all core plugins to use plugin.json instead of
    getInformation() [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #8065)
  * Warning: imagecopyresampled() expects parameter 2 to be resource,
    string given (Closes: #8028)
  * Force html templates to reload when development mode is enabled [by
    @tsteur, @mnapoli] (Closes: #8019)
  * Moved i18n data to core/Intl [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7996)
  * Implement HTTP-Authentication for transport methods socket & fopen
    [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #7980)
  * No way to get sites without group using the reporting API [by
    @alexkuk] (Closes: #7975)
  * Detect monitor.us as a bot (Closes: #7972)
  * Add a divider after the Visitors in Real-time header (Closes: #7965)
  * with success -> successfully [by @dandv, @sgiehl] (Closes: #7936)
  * List of devices under "visitors" is very near to 10 and does not
    require a pager (Closes: #7920)
  * Require TCPDF using composer [by @sgiehl] (Closes: #7908)
  * Visitorlog: Use a tooltip to display additional information to avoid
    text truncation [by @sgiehl, @mattab] (Closes: #7907)
  * Visit Overview (with graph) widget targets correct graph [by
    @spacenate, @tsteur] (Closes: #7872)
  * Create UI tests for ImageGraph plugin so testing can be automated
    (to some level) [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #7859)
  * update pchart library from 2.1.3 to 2.1.4 and moved them to a new
    folder [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7844)
  * Restore auth when calling API only if needed [by @tsteur, @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7804)
  * Make website manager take 100% of width on a big screen [by @tsteur,
    @mnapoli] (Closes: #7775)
  * Refactoring CronArchive setup + use for less technical debt [by
    @diosmosis, @mnapoli] (Closes: #7707)
  * Injection Inception, Final cleanup of test environment setup [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #8027)
  * Injection Inception, Add Access and Auth objects to DI [by
    @diosmosis, @mnapoli] (Closes: #8026)
  * Injection Inception, Using DI as primary mechanism in setting up
    Test environment [by @diosmosis, @mnapoli] (Closes: #8008)
  * Injection Inception, Allow integration + system tests to override DI
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #7963)
  * Injection Inception, Adding Config to DI [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #7957)
  * Moby DIoC: Piwik environment encapsulation [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #7644)
  * Add date to CronArchive output when printing info about
    preprocessing what will be archived for. [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #8214)
  * Test to make sure we do not break the external widget URL API [by
    @tsteur] (Closes: #8221)
  * Warning - preg_match(): Unknown modifier 'a' [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #8290)
  * Installer should let you bypass the "optional" file integrity check
    [by @mattab] (Closes: #8264)
  * Sites Manager doesn't save or show some saved global settings
    (Closes: #8247)
  * Show "Keyword" dimension name in All websites > Search Engine [by
    @sgiehl] (Closes: #8201)
  * Using setCookiesPath creates 2 cookies [by @parruc] (Closes: #8112)
  * Email address hel*lo@mail.com should be accepted as valid [by
    @diosmosis] (Closes: #7298)
  * Add some SearchEngine Hostnames [by @pebosi, @mattab] (Closes:
    #8250)
  * add constant PIWIK_VENDOR_PATH [by @craue, @mattab] (Closes: #8227)
  * Replaced inline style with stylesheet in add email report form [by
    @Fensterbank, @mattab] (Closes: #8207)
  * Speeding up javascript tests 2.5 times [by @barbushin, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #8206)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 215 strings in 13 languages
    (am, ar, de, el, es, fi, nb, nl, pl, sv, fr, ru, da) [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #7871)
  * [automatic translation update] Updated 104 strings in 43 languages
    (bn, sv, ru, bs, ca, cs, cy, el, et, eu, fa, fi, fr, gl, he, hi, hr,
    hu, id, is, it, ja, ka, ko, lt, lv, nb, nl, nn, pl, pt, ro, sk, sl,
