piwik (2.13.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.13.1
  * Regression: MultiSites.getAll does not handle showColumns correct
    [by @diosmosis] (Closes: #7818)
  * Report date to load by default doesn't work [by @mnapoli] (Closes:
    #7795)
  * $userPreferences->getDefaultReport() gives Empty String when not
    set. [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7839)
  * Goal url parameter is wrong when generating the image tracking code
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7829)
  * All websites dashboard lists website names double encoded [by
    @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes: #7806)
  * Can't add new site after update to 2.13.0 [by @diosmosis, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7802)
