piwik (2.11.1-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.11.1
  * Mysql process list is clogged with very inefficient updates on the
    archive blob tables [by @mattab] (Closes: #7195)
  * error in statistics graph, avg_time = 2 [by @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #7247)
  * Adding segment name in Scheduled email report title [by @ArnY,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7243)
  * Make widgets load faster on Piwik dashboard, and sparklines load
    faster on All Websites [by @ThaDafinser, @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7104)
  * Move language report to location reports [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7226)
  * Adding Toppreise.ch as search engine [by @sgiehl, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #7216)
  * Allow usernames with 2 letters [by @mattab] (Closes: #7121)
  * Move phpunit.xml.dist to phpunit.xml in PHPUnit bootstrap or when
    executing tests [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6635)
  * JavaScript Tracking Code: when a checkbox is clicked, make it clear
    the JS code was updated [by @mattab] (Closes: #7251)
  * Date Range Selector partially hidden in Dashboard (Closes: #7261)
  * DevicesDetection: Warning - array_key_exists() [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #7258)
  * The parameter 'period' isn't set in the Request, and a default value
    wasn't provided. when clicking on API link in menu [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7250)
  * When loading URL and not logged in, this should load the login form
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #7193)
  * Forced French translation even with English setting [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7187)
  * System check not verifying permissions for LOAD DATA INFILE [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #7185)
  * Correctly process unique visitors across websites in MetaSite [by
    @mattab] (Closes: #7244)

 -- Aurélien Requiem <aurelien@requiem.fr>  Sat, 28 Mar 2015 20:46:51 +1100

piwik (2.11.0-1) stable; urgency=high

  * Releasing Piwik 2.11.0
  * Log Analytics: Monitor Bandwidth for each page, download, and
    measure overall traffic in bytes [by @tsteur, @diosmosis] (Closes:
    #5248)
  * Release a Android SDK for Piwik - Mobile App Analytics (Closes:
    #4733)
  * New icon in all reports: let me segment by visitors matching this
    row's criteria [by @tsteur] (Closes: #4633)
  * Review guides at developer.piwik.org for official launch (Closes:
    #4456)
  * Visitor log may be displayed with many columns [by @sgiehl] (Closes:
    #6928)
  * duplicate entries in piwik_log_action leading to pages not visible
    in segments + provide means to fix duplicates [by @diosmosis]
    (Closes: #6436)
  * New User menu now similar to admin menu [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6989)
  * Add new segment Operating System Version (Closes: #7206)
  * Splitted referrers overview into "Overview" and "All Referrers" [by
    @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6945)
  * Split goals and ecommerce in two menus, and Manage Goals via User
    menu [by @tsteur, @mattab] (Closes: #6944)
  * When User ID is used, set the first party cookie UUID to this User
    ID [by @jantlwoomy, @mattab] (Closes: #7167)
  * Add option to map API tracking parameter to custom variable in log
    importer script. [by @diosmosis, @mattab] (Closes: #7151)
  * Provide a way to specify an alternate whois provider - SEO plugin
    [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7107)
  * For new installs, do not use the Anonymized IP addresses when
    enriching visits [by @mattab] (Closes: #7229)
  * when main Menu is focused, display submenu [by @TheCrowsJoker,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7026)
  * Make email reports more beautiful [by @mattab, @munro98] (Closes:
    #6988)
  * Tweaks to improve accessibility (section around graph, better
    tooltip, set language in html) [by @itscutekk, @mattab] (Closes:
    #7024)
  * Improved accessibility by putting offscreen text in the widget title
    [by @munro98, @mattab] (Closes: #7022)
  * Added h3 tags to widget headers (accessibility) [by @TheCrowsJoker,
    @mattab] (Closes: #7015)
  * Changed colours for better accessibility for people with sight
    difficulties [by @flodrwho] (Closes: #7011)
  * Improved accessibility with off-screen text added on the menu [by
    @munro98, @mattab] (Closes: #7038)
  * Piwik Installation now fits with the current piwik style [by
    @TheCrowsJoker, @mattab] (Closes: #7037)
  * See the focus of menu items when tabbing through the page
    (accessibility) [by @TheCrowsJoker, @mattab] (Closes: #7035)
  * Add "Skip to content" feature when user presses tab key
    (accessibility) [by @flodrwho, @mattab] (Closes: #7025)
  * Improve Login Screen Layout - input width. [by @patagonic, @mnapoli]
    (Closes: #7102)
  * When development mode is enabled, add a new language that shows raw
    translation id [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #7094)
  * As a user I want to configure purging of processed custom ranges [by
    @mgazdzik] (Closes: #7079)
  * Improve Login Screen Layout [by @patagonic, @tsteur] (Closes: #7074)
  * Changes for usage of DeviceDetector 3.0 [by @sgiehl, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #7068)
  * Refactored Twig templates using a single base layout [by @mnapoli,
    @tsteur] (Closes: #7040)
  * Segment dropdown enhancements [by @Irrational86, @mattab] (Closes:
    #6958)
  * New Piwik Ini component [by @mnapoli, @mattab] (Closes: #6939)
  * Add Administrator link to top menu [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6937)
  * Move "Anonymous user settings" into a separate page and menu item
    [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6935)
  * Rename plugin management commands [by @mnapoli] (Closes: #6915)
  * include server time (as timestamp) in visitor actions (visitor live
    API) [by @FelixSchwarz, @mattab] (Closes: #6814)
  * Add a search field in Visitor settings Browsers [by @sgiehl]
    (Closes: #6490)
  * Force new visit after midnight [by @tsteur] (Closes: #6217)
  * Improve performance by caching all translations in a flat array
    (Closes: #6060)
  * Introduce Dependency Injection [by @sabl0r] (Closes: #4917)
  * add a plugin description to all core plugins [by @mattab] (Closes:
    #7184)
