  * Add name parameter to MenuTop. [by @czolnowski, @tsteur] (Closes:
    #5858)
  * Treat response with any 2xx status code as successful POST track
    request [by @sslavic, @mattab] (Closes: #5859)
  * Show the image description also as title [by @ThaDafinser, @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5861)
