    #5866)
  * Unable to use new domain extensions as an email address [by @tsteur]
    (Closes: #5867)
  * remove dead code [by @craue, @tsteur] (Closes: #5871)
  * code cleanup [by @craue, @tsteur] (Closes: #5872)
